song.title: Transplanetary Cruise
song.info:
Transplanetary cruise written by TOALNKOR of REALTECH For the party report
Hahahahaha....No original samples, but all ripped from Skaven / FC ....
In 2196 AD, an huge ship called Rama II flew close to the earth. A crew from the A.S.I. Had to explore It. As the starship left our solar system, three people were still on board. They are still alive, but On a transplanetary cruise!
Greetings fly to CORINNE and MURIEL, Silent mode / Pentagon, Skaven / FC, Purple motion / FC, Tonedeaf & Gibson / Extr. ,Stargazer, Cybelius and Mellow-d / Sonic, Moog & Shad / Infiny, Moby, Ryan Cramer / Renaissance, Zodiak / Cascada, Leinad / Avalanche, My class (TS3)
Written on 27/2/1995 Tune length --> 4:14 mins
Enjoy this track. TN out.
